{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Driving Test Simulation</h2>Either you are an experienced driver, or a driving student, the Chinese Driving Simulator will provide you with a complete Chinese driving test experience. It will show you the rules, help you understand the process of the driving test.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Real Testing Center</h2>The testing road and routes are based on real testing center in QingDao, China. The game provides players with a realistic testing condition with driving AIs as other testing cars and cars passing by.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Subject 1, 4</h2>The game provides complete test bank of subject 1 and subject4, which are written test sections in the Chinese driving test. The UI and design are based on real testing screen, to help players prepare for the written tests<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Subject 2</h2>The game includes 4 sections of the subject 2 road test, reverse parking, parallel parking, curve driving and quarter turn, it provides a tutorial to help player understand and learn the subject 2 test.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Subject 3</h2>The game includes the subject 3 road test, which is similar to the road test in the United States, but with more strict rules. The game will provide player with tutorial to understand the test process and rules.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1815440?t=1672190611","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1815440?t=1672190611","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815440/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1672190611","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815440/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1672190611","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>Check this game!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Driving Test Simulation</h2>Either you are an experienced driver, or a driving student, the Chinese Driving Simulator will provide you with a complete Chinese driving test experience. It will show you the rules, help you understand the process of the driving test.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Real Testing Center</h2>The testing road and routes are based on real testing center in QingDao, China. The game provides players with a realistic testing condition with driving AIs as other testing cars and cars passing by.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Subject 1, 4</h2>The game provides complete test bank of subject 1 and subject4, which are written test sections in the Chinese driving test. The UI and design are based on real testing screen, to help players prepare for the written tests<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Subject 2</h2>The game includes 4 sections of the subject 2 road test, reverse parking, parallel parking, curve driving and quarter turn, it provides a tutorial to help player understand and learn the subject 2 test.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Subject 3</h2>The game includes the subject 3 road test, which is similar to the road test in the United States, but with more strict rules. The game will provide player with tutorial to understand the test process and rules.","developers":["Lawliet"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Racing","id":"9"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815440/header.jpg?t=1672190611","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256862402,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256862402/movie480.mp4?t=1638107418","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256862402/movie_max.mp4?t=1638107418"},"name":"subject3","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256862402/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1638107418","webm"